\section{Conclusion}

We have presented a fundamental reinterpretation of universal constants as emergent patterns of perpetron-qualiton field excitations in the $\mathbb{R}^7$ manifold. By replacing arbitrary free parameters with structured binary excitation patterns, we transform constants from inexplicable inputs to physics into algorithmic outputs of a self-computing universe governed by the piece computer.

